content.rendered:
Directed by Sukumar.

Written by Sukumar. Buchi Babu Sana. Srinivas Rongali. Vikram Juthika. Hussain Sha Kiran.

Cast N.T. Rama Rao Jr.(Abhiram (as Junior N.T.R.)). Rakul Preet Singh(Divyanka). Jagapathi Babu(Krishnamurthy). Rajendra Prasad(Abhiram’s Father (as Rajendraprasad)). Rajeev Kanakala(Abhiram’s Brother (as Rajiv Kanakala)). Liza van der Smissen(Kate) . Darien Asian(Street Protester). Srinivas Avasarala(Abhiram’s Brother). Nadia Awan(Wife). Joy Badlani(Doctor Aravindha). Kishore Bhatt(Businessman). Rene Costa(Angry investor). Simona Crugnola(Cafe Diner / Clubber / Businessman’s Assistant). Daniel Eghan(Bodyguard). Vajja Venkata Giridhar(Giri). Ashish Gole(Boy 1). Ernest Gromov(Gang Leader). Lee Nicholas Harris(Police Sgt). Noni Harrison(Lead Angry Protestor). Sammy Jonas Heaney(Dancer (as Sam Heaney)). Sharif Islam(Conference Businessman). Alex Jaep(Waiter). Jemiyah(Hospital Receptionist).Jackson Kai. Adnan Kapadia(Dr. Patel). Vaunisha Kapoor(Women Chasing Film Star). Phelim Kelly(Street Protester). Mudassar Saeed Khan(Angry Protester). Ksenia Kirkham(Personal assistant).Vennela Kishore. Richard Bhakti Klein(Head of Spanish Inspection Team (as R. Bhakti Klein)). Joelle Koissi(Servant). Mervi Koski(Restaurant Customer). Caroline Koziol(Receptionist). Dimple Kumar(Angry Protester). Theresa Lamb(Angry Mob Member). Cristian Lazar(Street Protester). Adam Lazarus(Surgeon). Swaylee Loughnane(Butler).Madhoo. Alpesh Malaviya(Angry Protestor / Street Gangster). Timothy McDevitt(Bodyguard). Shaikh Mirza(Fighter).Naveen Neni. Geoffrey Osborne(Hotel Guest).Thagubothu Ramesh. Andrea Ravera(Spanish Inspector). Anil Sanchania(Angry Businessman). Anna Satchit(Angry Protestor). Noel Sean(Noel). Atul Sharma(Billionaire Businessman). Vinita Sharma(Angry Protestor). Shenturan(Hotel Manager).Sithara. Amit Tiwari(Amit). Ashish Vidyarthi(Satpal Singh / Kapil Singh). Jo Wheatley(Street protester)

Language Telugu.

Producers Sudheer Edara. Narravula Gopi Krishna. B.V.S.N. Prasad. Padavala Nageswar Rao. Sudipto Sarkar. Kumar Siddam Vijay.

Production Reliance Entertainment. Sri Venkateswara Cine Chitra.
